Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:56.50,百乃工-CN-only,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\an9\fs56\c&HFEFEFE&\3c&HD5B7FE&\\\fscx400\fscy400\p1\bord4\1a&H55&\4a&HFF&\pos(1898,20)}m 0 0 l  90 0 90 80 0 80{\p0}
